high_descs: Turn right and walk to the TV.
Pick up the bowl from the TV stand.
Turn around and face the coffee table.
Set the bowl down on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Set the bowl on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the chair at the end of the room, then turn right again and go to the TV.
Pick up the grey bowl on the left corner of the entertainment stand.
Turn around and walk to the right side of the coffee table.
Place the grey bowl on the left side of the yellow vase, on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Place a grey bowl next to the yellow vase, on the coffee table.

high_descs: Cross the room and go to the right to face the television.
Pick the gray bowl up from in front of the television.
Turn around to face the glass and black table.
Put the bowl down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a table on a bowl.
